{"tid":1792251,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方相信昨晚檢獲AR15長距離步槍是不法分子自行組裝","createTime":"2019-12-21T13:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T13:28:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe398803f940afd7f6e96df906969b2fb26897cd","tid":1792251,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名男子昨晚在大埔被警員截查時開了一槍，警方其後檢獲兩支槍及二百多發子彈，警方相信檢獲的槍械是自行組裝，並與本月初民陣遊行前搗破武器庫的案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科警司劉肇邦：「警方檢獲的AR15長距離步槍，初步檢查相信是不法分子自行組裝，入面有超過二百發子彈，其中有六十一發更是裝在環型快速入彈器內。警方在周五晚及十二月八日，分別檢獲兩枝手槍，同屬P80型號而周五晚被捕的男子正是十二月八日案中的通輯犯。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374197&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3ANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=842a76a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374197&h=5e90f22c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374197</a>"},{"pid":"7d9afdf01b20f6ed5f6d3d3f7b178eb6d43a4ae6","tid":1792251,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"Popo自認不法分子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038586fa04bd4f9669e4b42b50c0faa9cdf87937","tid":1792251,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"聽日有行動幫手推！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5Mi7yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5Mi7yZ.jpg&h=cc26222d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJYhDFF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJYhDFF.jpg&h=6b898915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［主線任務］聽日1530嘅維吾爾族集會獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55f5f1232a7ee